  "id": "019d286a-f2d7-7750-81b8-10a17e25fcff",
  "content": "## Toggle Command Interface\n\n### Enable Flow\n\n1. Check `nvidia-smi` is accessible (fail with guidance if not)\n2. Install CUDA toolkit + cuDNN via apt if not present\n3. Download `corvia-inference-cuda-linux-amd64` from GitHub releases\n4. Replace `/usr/local/bin/corvia-inference` (backup CPU version as `corvia-inference-cpu`)\n5. Set flag `cuda=enabled`\n6. Restart `corvia-inference` if running\n\n\n### Disable Flow\n\n1. Restore CPU binary from backup\n2. Set flag `cuda=disabled`\n3. Restart `corvia-inference` if running\n",
